metadata.name: Azuki: CORRUPT3D
metadata.description:
A derivative art of ChipNFT's Azuki #8769, #6993 and #5629.
I have no intention of distorting or desecrating the original design of any Azuki and ChipNFT, the holder, I just want to express creativity in my own way.

This artwork will be listed by the end of ChipNFT's Azuki contest.
